{"title":"CSS —— 预处理器","date":"2019-11-25T08:51:51.945Z","thumbnail":"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/11/25/Mv9V58.md.jpg","link":"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor","updated":"2019-11-26T02:27:21.100Z","content":"<p>CSS预处理器是基于CSS的另外一种语言，通过工具编译成CSS。它添加了很多CSS不具备的属性，能够提升CSS文件组织。主要流行的有：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>less</li>\n<li>sass/scss</li>\n</ul>\n<p>提供的功能：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>嵌套 反映层级和约束</li>\n<li>变量和计算 减少重复代码</li>\n<li>Extend和Mixin 代码片段</li>\n<li>循环 使用于复杂有规律的形式</li>\n<li>import CSS文件模块化</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"嵌套\">嵌套<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#嵌套\"></a></h2><p>&amp;: 平级，其他的使用就是按层级写</p>\n<h2 id=\"变量\">变量<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#变量\"></a></h2><p>less中：@变量名: 值(带变量值)</p>\n<p>sass中：$变量名: 值(带变量名) </p>\n<h2 id=\"mixin\">mixin<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#mixin\"></a></h2><p>在CSS中对样式进行复用，可以通过参数控制复用形式。</p>\n<p>In less：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight less\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.block</span>(<span class=\"variable\">@fontSize</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">font-size</span>:<span class=\"variable\">@fontSize</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//使用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.nav</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.block</span>(<span class=\"variable\">@fontSize</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>In sass：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight scss\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@<span class=\"keyword\">mixin</span> block(<span class=\"variable\">$fontSize</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">font-size</span>:<span class=\"variable\">$fontSize</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//使用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.nav</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  @<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> block(<span class=\"variable\">$fontSize</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"extend\">extend<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#extend\"></a></h2><p>在CSS中对样式进行复用，但是可以减少编译后的重复代码。</p>\n<p>In less：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight less\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.nav</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:extend(.block)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ...</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>In scss：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight scss\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@<span class=\"keyword\">extend</span> .block&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ...</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"loop\">loop<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#loop\"></a></h2><p>按照一定的规则循环生成一系列CSS代码。适用于复杂且有规律的样式。</p>\n<p>In less：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight less\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.gen-col</span>(<span class=\"variable\">@n</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">when</span> (<span class=\"variable\">@n</span>&gt;<span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.gen-col</span>(<span class=\"variable\">@n-1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.col-</span><span class=\"variable\">@&#123;n&#125;</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">1000px</span>/<span class=\"number\">12</span>*<span class=\"variable\">@n</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.gen-col</span>(<span class=\"number\">12</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>In sass：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight scss\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@<span class=\"keyword\">mixin</span> gen-col(<span class=\"variable\">$n</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  if <span class=\"variable\">$n</span>&gt;0 &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    @<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> gen-col(<span class=\"variable\">$n-1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"selector-class\">.col-</span>#&#123;<span class=\"variable\">$n</span>&#125;&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">1000px</span>/<span class=\"number\">12</span>*<span class=\"variable\">$n</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">@<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> gen-col(<span class=\"number\">12</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">//更简单</span><br><span class=\"line\">@<span class=\"keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"variable\">$i</span> from 1 through 12 &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.col-</span>#&#123;<span class=\"variable\">$i</span>&#125; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">1000px</span>/<span class=\"number\">12</span>*<span class=\"variable\">$i</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"import\">import<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#import\"></a></h2><p>实现CSS代码模块化。</p>\n<p>In less/sass：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight less\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">@import</span> <span class=\"string\">\"...\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"预处理器框架\">预处理器框架<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#预处理器框架\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li>SASS - Compass</li>\n<li>Less - lesshat/EST</li>\n<li>提供现成的mixin</li>\n<li>类似JS类库，封装常用功能</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"面试题\">面试题<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor#面试题\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li>常见的CSS预处理器</li>\n<li>预处理器的作用<ul>\n<li>帮助更好地组织CSS代码</li>\n<li>提高代码的复用率</li>\n<li>提升可维护性</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>预处理器能力</li>\n<li>预处理器的优缺点<ul>\n<li>优点：提高代码复用率和可维护性</li>\n<li>缺点：需要引入编译过程，有学习成本</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS —— 工程化","link":"2019/11/26/CSS-engineering"},"next":{"title":"CSS —— 动画","link":"2019/11/25/CSS-animation"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/11/25/CSS-preprocessor/","toc":[{"title":"嵌套","id":"嵌套","index":"1"},{"title":"变量","id":"变量","index":"2"},{"title":"mixin","id":"mixin","index":"3"},{"title":"extend","id":"extend","index":"4"},{"title":"loop","id":"loop","index":"5"},{"title":"import","id":"import","index":"6"},{"title":"预处理器框架","id":"预处理器框架","index":"7"},{"title":"面试题","id":"面试题","index":"8"}]}